title: Prodigy Game | Springfest is back - PLAY NOW!
author: Prodigy Game
description:
Prodigy Springfest is back with even more ways to enjoy the return of Spring! Login to Prodigy today and head to Lamplight Town to get started on your Springfest adventure!

Springfest brings you daily challenges, new rewards, and exclusive items to collect! Choose between the Fox Knights and Bunny Bandits in Lamplight town and see what surprises lay ahead. Visit Prodigy Game today:
https://bit.ly/3seB8pV
